  <section id="users" class="section-padding wow fadeInUp delay-05s">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <h3 class ="pad-bt15">Attending a Conference?</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <div class ="centered-icon navy-text"><i class="fa fa-magic fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Automatic Profile Generation</h3>
            <p>Upload the URL of your personal academic website. We'll automatically collect your publication history.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <div class="service-item">
            <div class ="centered-icon navy-text"><i class="fa fa-address-card-o fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
            <h3>Personalized Recommendation</h3>
            <p>Our machine learning algorithm computes the similarity between all of your publication collection and
              the papers presented at the conferences you sign up for. Based on this similarity and your past
              preferences, we generate a list of lectures that align with your interests. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <div class ="centered-icon navy-text"><i class="fa fa-calendar fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Integrated Scheduler</h3>
            <p>Based on your personalized recommendations, we generate an optimized schedule for you to attend your
              top-recommended lectures and presentations. PairCon &copy; integrates with all major calendars so you can
              see your schedule in one place. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="bottom-line">
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
          <h2 class="service-title pad-bt50">Organizing a Conference?</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <div class ="centered-icon navy-text"><i class="fa fa-users fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Manage Attendees</h3>
            <p>See who is attending your conference and get a headcount on which lectures will be in high demand</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <div class="service-item">
            <div class ="centered-icon navy-text"><i class="fa fa-refresh fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
            <h3>One-Click Conference Generation</h3>
            <p>Submit the URL of your conference page and we'll automatically collect the publications presented to
              compute personalized recommendations for attendees. Want to upload the lecture schedule? We'll
              automatically integrate that into our optimized scheduler too. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <div class ="centered-icon navy-text"><i class="fa fa-info-circle fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Centralized Information</h3>
            <p>Upload the conference schedule, website, map, contact info, and more to display on one centralized page. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
